---
// Email Capture - early signup CTA with Netlify Forms
---

<div class="email-capture" id="early-signup">
  <div class="container container--narrow">
    <p class="email-capture__text">
      GDP counts a cancer diagnosis as growth. We're building a better metric. Get your first briefing.
    </p>
    <form class="email-capture__form" id="early-email-form" data-netlify="true" name="email-capture" netlify-honeypot="bot-field" novalidate>
      <input type="hidden" name="form-name" value="email-capture" />
      <input type="text" name="bot-field" style="display:none" tabindex="-1" autocomplete="off">
      <input class="email-capture__input" type="email" id="early-email" name="email"
             placeholder="your@email.com" required aria-label="Email address" />
      <button class="email-capture__btn" type="submit">Get the Briefing</button>
    </form>
    <p class="email-capture__note">No spam. One email with the MIND framework + Zone Zero simulator. Unsubscribe anytime.</p>
    <p class="email-capture__success" id="early-email-success" role="alert">
      Check your inbox. Your first briefing is on the way.
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
